title: Youtube Client
description:
This is a awesome Youtube-Client!

You dont need a brower anymore to watch videos in HD and WITHOUT LAGGS!

You can access your YouTube Channel and you can upload videos!

You can also write commets and enjoy Youtube with the community!

No Videoplayer crashes anymore!

There are much Themes like Dark-Theme etc. and an Theme editor wich let you customize your own look of Youtube!

It has a more nice interface of the subscribed channels than the normal Brower-Youtube

There are some Youtube Bots included.

This is the new way to enjoy Youtube

User Ratings:

"This is awesome...no laggs and my youtube looks so nice after i cutomized it"

"Wooooohooo. This is the best thing i've ever seen"

"Who needs Firefox and Chrome anymore? :P I just use this client for now"



Start now your Experience with the Youtube-Client and push the download button!
